=head1 DESCRIPTION

Specifies the Amazon S3 bucket where DataSync uploads your task report
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/datasync/latest/userguide/task-reports.html).

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> BucketAccessRoleArn => Str

Specifies the Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the IAM policy that allows
DataSync to upload a task report to your S3 bucket. For more
information, see Allowing DataSync to upload a task report to an Amazon
S3 bucket
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/datasync/latest/userguide/task-reports.html).


=head2 B<REQUIRED> S3BucketArn => Str

Specifies the ARN of the S3 bucket where DataSync uploads your report.


=head2 Subdirectory => Str

Specifies a bucket prefix for your report.



